<body>
<img src="http://190.0.34.154:3013/images/frame.png"/>
<div align="justify" style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;">
  <br/><br/>
  Medellin, <%=Time.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d")%><br/><br/>
  <strong>Señor(a): <%=@user.nombre rescue nil%><br/><br/></strong>
  Cordialmente se le informa que se ha registrado una reserva segun la siguiente información:
</div><br/>
<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse">
  <tr valign="middle">
    <td width="30%" height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Fecha requerida del servicio</strong></td>
    <td width="70%" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.fecha.strftime("%Y-%m-%d") rescue nil %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Vehiculo</strong></td>
    <td style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.vehiculo.placa rescue nil %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Conductor</strong></td>
    <td style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.vehiculo.nombre rescue nil %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Telefono Conductor</strong></td>
    <td style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.vehiculo.celular rescue nil %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr class="odd1">
    <td height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Hora Inicial</strong></td>
    <td style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.vehiculoshorario.descripcion rescue nil %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Hora Final</strong></td>
    <td style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.horafinvehiculo rescue nil %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr class="odd1">
    <td height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Usuario responsable servicio</strong></td>
    <td style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.responsable rescue nil%></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Numero de personas</strong></td>
    <td style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.nro_pasajeros %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr class="odd1">
    <td height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Destino</strong></td>
    <td style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.destino%></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td height="20" style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>Creación de la solicitud</strong></td>
    <td style="border:1px solid #000000; font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=@vehiculosprogramacion.updated_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %X") rescue nil%> - <%=@vehiculosprogramacion.solicitante rescue nil%></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<br/><br/>
<div style="font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><strong>S I F I - Sistema de Informacion ISVIMED</strong></div>
<br/>
<strong style="font-size: 11px; font-family: Tahoma;"><%=Time.now.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %X")%></strong>
